TITLE: Tokio TCP Read Function with Race Condition Handling
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates a Tokio TCP read function that handles potential race conditions between reading data and clearing readiness events. It uses a loop to await readiness, attempts to read, and manages errors, including the `WouldBlock` case.

SOURCE: https://github.com/tokio-rs/tokio/blob/master/tokio/docs/reactor-refactor.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: rust
CODE:
